column2:
"This place is huge. Big enough to fit a race of
dragorii, I guess. Searching it blindly like this is
starting to seem a little ambitious."

"So, what do you say we start hunting for the
kind of dragorii who might be feeling chatty?"

"Huh? What's that sound? And is it getting
closer?"

"Points for you, Echo. Also, you might want to
get your weapon out.
You, too, <%me>!"
"A dragorii?! It doesn't look chatty to me!"

"Argh, it's the D-arker taint. We've got no choice but
to fight!"

"やっぱ龍族が住んでるだけあって
広いところだよな、ここは。
何のアテもなしに探すのは、ちと骨か。"

"さて、どこかに話を聞けそうな
龍族サンはいないかな、っと。"

"……ん？　なんだろ、この音。
何か、迫ってきてるような……？"

"……お手柄だぜ、エコー。
ついでに、武器も構えとけ。
<%me>もだ！"

"りゅ、龍族！？
様子が尋常じゃないけど……！"

"……くそったれ！
ダーカーの影響を受けてやがるな！
やるしかないぞ！"
